<p>Despair's advantage is achieved<br>
By suffering — Despair —<br>
To be assisted of Reverse<br>
One must Reverse have bore —<br>
<br>
The Worthiness of Suffering like<br>
The Worthiness of Death<br>
Is ascertained by tasting —<br>
<br>
As can no other Mouth<br>
<br>
Of Savors — make us conscious —<br>
As did ourselves partake —<br>
Affliction feels impalpable<br>
Until Ourselves are struck —</p>